all your apples

19:56.896 --> 19:57.964
for the festival,

19:58.064 --> 19:59.266
there are none
left for you.

19:59.366 --> 20:02.335
Yeah, that's too bad but--
Lucky for you,

20:02.435 --> 20:04.671
I have plenty more
back at the orchard.

20:04.771 --> 20:06.806
I can have three bushels
to you by morning.

20:06.906 --> 20:08.841
