20:08.941 --> 20:11.143
(sighing)
Timmy,

20:11.244 --> 20:15.415
you know when people say
honesty is the best policy?

20:15.515 --> 20:17.450
Well, this is hard
to tell you but...

20:17.550 --> 20:19.386
You can tell me
anything, Sunny.

20:19.486 --> 20:22.188
We're friends.
It's been so nice of you

20:22.289 --> 20:23.656
to bring us apples

20:23.756 --> 20:25.758
and we're very grateful.

20:25.858 --> 20:28.194
But I have to ask you to stop.

20:28.295 --> 20:31.063
Really? Why?

20:31.163 --> 20:33.232
We had so many apples,
we couldn't fit them

20:33.333 --> 20:34.934
in the salon anymore.

20:35.034 --> 20:36.269
I should've said something,

20:36.369 --> 20:38.471
but I didn't want
to hurt your feelings.

20:38.571 --> 20:40.407
(gasping)

20:41.808 --> 20:43.276
I hope you're not upset.

20:43.376 --> 20:45.778
Or hurt. Or angry.

20:45.878 --> 20:48.648
Or all three.

20:48.748 --> 20:50.149
Whew.

20:50.249 --> 20:52.051
Thank goodness.

20:52.151 --> 20:53.386
What?

20:53.486 --> 20:55.855
I can finally stop
picking apples.

20:55.955 --> 20:57.189
I kept bringing
them because

20:57.290 --> 20:59.158
I thought you
liked them so much.

20:59.258 --> 21:00.993
Really? I guess
it would've

21:01.093 --> 21:03.996
just been better if we all just
said what we were feeling.

21:04.096 --> 21:05.798
But I'm glad
you told me, Sunny.

21:05.898 --> 21:08.568
And to show there
are no hard feelings,

21:08.668 --> 21:11.904
my peach trees will
start blooming soon.

21:12.004 --> 21:13.973
I can bring you
a couple bushels

21:14.073 --> 21:15.942
as soon as they're ripe.

21:16.042 --> 21:17.777
(girls gasping)

21:17.877 --> 21:20.580
(cackling)

21:20.680 --> 21:22.782
I'm just kidding.

21:22.882 --> 21:25.051
